name: SINCO
description:
))) SOUND ON (((

I hear it, something of a futuristic bamboo forest

No, no way, why would they have bamboos in space?

- Have you ever seen how fast that thing grows? You can double your spaceship every week

- - And the vases are weightless, you can bring a huge tree with you on a leash.

- - - But bamboos are light here on earth and no one does that.

- - - - It will be a space thing I garantee you.
